---
import { Terminal, ExternalLink } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<footer class="relative z-10 bg-surface border-t border-white/5 pt-20 pb-10">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-16">
      
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="p-2 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-brand-magenta">
              <Terminal class="h-6 w-6" />
          </div>
          <span class="font-black text-2xl tracking-tighter text-white uppercase leading-none">
            Arkania<span class="text-brand-magenta">Host</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-slate-400 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
            Infraestructura de alto rendimiento diseñada por gamers, para gamers. Sin lag, sin sobreventa y con soporte que realmente juega lo que hostea.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-7 space-y-6">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Accesos Rápidos</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li>
            <a href="https://panel.arkaniahost.xyz" target="_blank" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group">
              Panel de Control <ExternalLink size={12} class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"/>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://billing.arkaniahost.xyz" target="_blank" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group">
              Área de Clientes <ExternalLink size={12} class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"/>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li><a href="https://status.arkaniahost.xyz" target="_blank" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors">Estado de la Red</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://billing.arkaniahost.xyz/tickets/create" target="_blank" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors">Abrir Ticket</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Legal</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li><a href="/legal/terms" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors">Términos de Servicio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/legal/privacy" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors">Política de Privacidad</a></li>
          <li><a href="/legal/refunds" class="hover:text-brand-magenta transition-colors">Política de Reembolsos</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Comunidad</h4>
        <a 
          href="https://discord.gg/arkania" 
          target="_blank" 
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#5865F2]/10 border border-[#5865F2]/20 rounded-lg text-[#5865F2] hover:bg-[#5865F2] hover:text-white transition-all group w-full justify-center"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 127.14 96.36" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
            <path d="M107.7,8.07A105.15,105.15,0,0,0,81.47,0a72.06,72.06,0,0,0-3.36,6.83A97.68,97.68,0,0,0,49,6.83,72.37,72.37,0,0,0,45.64,0,105.89,105.89,0,0,0,19.39,8.09C2.71,32.65-1.82,56.6.39,80.21a105.73,105.73,0,0,0,32.77,16.15,77.7,77.7,0,0,0,7.07-11.39,67.42,67.42,0,0,1-11.45-5.39c.91-.64,1.81-1.31,2.65-2a75.79,75.79,0,0,0,62,0c.84.69,1.74,1.36,2.66,2a67.41,67.41,0,0,1-11.48,5.41,80.7,80.7,0,0,0,7.09,11.39,105.09,105.09,0,0,0,32.81-16.14C129.58,52.84,124.92,28.9,107.7,8.07ZM42.45,65.69C36.18,65.69,31,60,31,53s5.07-12.65,11.41-12.65S54,46,53.86,53,48.72,65.69,42.45,65.69Zm42.24,0C78.41,65.69,73.25,60,73.25,53s5.07-12.65,11.44-12.65S96.23,46,96.11,53,91,65.69,84.69,65.69Z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">Discord</span>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 text-center">
      <div class="text-[12px] font-mono text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} ArkaniaHost, LLC | Todos los derechos reservados
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>